{"tid":1181533,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[an/ios] Grand Summoners 國際版 哥布林殺手合作活動開始 & KOB團長登場","createTime":"2019-06-01T16:37:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T13:36:43.000Z","uid":174578,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"33aae66f6cb2175da8c8ddf8f1ddbdc6e458815c","tid":1181533,"uid":174578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T16:37:22.000Z","msg":"官網 <br />\n<a href=\"https://global.grandsummoners.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fglobal.grandsummoners.com%2F&d=77sZY8L1Q3njiwGc8u9yThyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=9832d51a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://global.grandsummoners.com/</a><br />\n而家可以在香港app store / play store 直接下載遊戲<br />\n遊戲係無中文版＋介面，全英文，最大支援４人協力<br />\n如果英文唔掂玩之前請三思！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fHhQANc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfHhQANc.jpg&h=680d39c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新手必看＋攻略＋５星卷交換推薦 新手想玩請花時間睇睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1flUT3ktN7vVZnsoQ06qIJ1PHrqlEJR4-81YnwkjxvbQ/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1flUT3ktN7vVZnsoQ06qIJ1PHrqlEJR4-81YnwkjxvbQ%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=77sZY8L1Q3njiwGc8u9yThyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=5b459035\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1flUT3ktN7vVZnsoQ06qIJ1PHrqlEJR4-81YnwkjxvbQ/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n首抽推薦表（逢維護後更新）<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/10OGCwC3WVPRdD0ge4-FRFyt4Q46ILkdqB7NS8gGf74k/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F10OGCwC3WVPRdD0ge4-FRFyt4Q46ILkdqB7NS8gGf74k%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=77sZY8L1Q3njiwGc8u9yThyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=0216d779\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/10OGCwC3WVPRdD0ge4-FRFyt4Q46ILkdqB7NS8gGf74k/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\nkekeke聊天板 24小時開放<br />\n<a href=\"https://kekeke.cc/grand_summoners\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkekeke.cc%2Fgrand_summoners&d=77sZY8L1Q3njiwGc8u9yThyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=4ae5e39c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kekeke.cc/grand_summoners</a><br />\n歡迎加入長駐，有乜需要幫手找我"},{"pid":"e61a09b532f4493e32cc37e1c9c11ddeb2c4afc1","tid":1181533,"uid":174578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T16:38:15.000Z","msg":"gameplay<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3xtOxkwRXBs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3xtOxkwRXBs&d=77sZY8L1Q3njiwGc8u9yThyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=53e00dc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3xtOxkwRXBs</a>"},{"pid":"b8efe78f0e2f96eecc2e9cdb6a7b4735b0cac2b2","tid":1181533,"uid":174578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T16:39:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新手問題集（FAQ） copy自LINE農會群組 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n①裝備的種類分別 <br />\n共五種(括號內為通稱) <br />\n1.物理傷害(紅色)：物理性的傷害攻擊，部分裝備會與相關角色的攻擊方式特效相同。 <br />\n2.魔法傷害(紫色)：魔法性的傷害攻擊，通常持續傷害時間較長，有較多的裝備附帶特殊效果或異常狀態) <br />\n3.治療/恢復(綠色)：補ＨＰ或治療異常。 <br />\n4.防禦(藍色)：減輕傷害 <br />\n5.援護/輔助/BUFF(黃色）：賦予角色增益效果。 <br />\n<br />\n②裝備相關說明： <br />\n每隻角色有不同的裝備攔位，各有對應的星等與顏色，星等必須相同或是低於才可進行裝備。 <br />\n而遊戲當中部份打造的裝備還算實用，如：光翔劍（外傳第一章取得製作書）、聖冠（外傳女主角第二章/五星）。 <br />\n裝備亦可透過部分活動副本、大型副本取得，部分甚至筆抽裝來的好。高星裝備基本上個有用途，抽裝不見得好，但有些還是很實用。 <br />\n<br />\n③強勢角色：睇上面我有講 <br />\n<br />\n④突破系統：吃相同的角色或裝備即可突破，但要留意，透過主線或活動副本取得的角色或裝備，突滿的所需數量與抽到的並不相同。 <br />\n裝備突破的效果：裝備CT加快。 <br />\n角色突破的效果：裝備欄位的星等提升（註：每隻角色有一定上限），可強化的額外數值也會上升。 <br />\n<br />\n⑤<span style=\"color: red;\">幸運值Ｌｕｃｋ： <br />\n有機會使關卡結算獎勵時增加物品數量/寶箱(1~3件)在獲得角色、物品畫面的下方可以找到Luck欄位。 <br />\n目前只能透過吃相同角色累加。 <br />\n幸運值99以下有機增加1寶箱。 <br />\n幸運值100必出2寶箱。<br />\n幸運值120必出3寶箱(只有房主才有) </span><br />\n<br />\n⑥角色的被動技能： <br />\n被動技能是被設定不變的，如主角的被動大家都是一樣的，故其他角色也會相同。可以透過部分裝備包含有被動技能的，顯示在角色右方的被動欄位。當然脫下了裝備，相關被動也會被移除(裝備的被動是跟著裝備的)。 <br />\n<br />\n⑦Break： <br />\n如同新手教學，打破break，進入到Break Time的時候，除了可以打斷王的動作，還能讓目標受到的傷害增加，部分BOSS也會因此解除某些增益BUFF。"},{"pid":"9e1ee14e9679bc69698c25c9aa3f4760cbe95098","tid":1181533,"uid":174578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T16:40:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://kekeke.cc/grand_summoners\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkekeke.cc%2Fgrand_summoners&d=77sZY8L1Q3njiwGc8u9yThyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=4ae5e39c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kekeke.cc/grand_summoners</a><br />\n24小時開放歡迎內進"},{"pid":"2d8260fcf954321e9c88bc1293036a16ef3ece69","tid":1181533,"uid":174578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T18:05:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://kekeke.cc/grand_summoners\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkekeke.cc%2Fgrand_summoners&d=77sZY8L1Q3njiwGc8u9yThyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=4ae5e39c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kekeke.cc/grand_summoners</a><br />\n24小時開放歡迎內進</blockquote>"},{"pid":"91ad85556259f3db2b756febe33bf4e3cb39bd64","tid":1181533,"uid":174578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T07:28:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://kekeke.cc/grand_summoners\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkekeke.cc%2Fgrand_summoners&d=77sZY8L1Q3njiwGc8u9yThyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=4ae5e39c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kekeke.cc/grand_summoners</a><br />\n24小時開放歡迎內進</blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"48818573d564b3ec2278a77253455cf6d477eec6","tid":1181533,"uid":174578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T15:45:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://kekeke.cc/grand_summoners\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkekeke.cc%2Fgrand_summoners&d=77sZY8L1Q3njiwGc8u9yThyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=4ae5e39c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kekeke.cc/grand_summoners</a><br />\n24小時開放歡迎內進</blockquote>"},{"pid":"268546efc4f20ab92a96d6d3640ce1f66665767a","tid":1181533,"uid":174578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T04:41:26.000Z","msg":"<strong></strong>"},{"pid":"0132e74ecd52d8671b9248f3f64685103145af24","tid":1181533,"uid":174578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T11:47:23.000Z","msg":"<em></em>"},{"pid":"f1c2efbd740ee33ae06ce8c0ca85f53967b30af1","tid":1181533,"uid":174578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T16:39:37.000Z","msg":"<del></del>"},{"pid":"79f36f8effc957c8208adb22b5d6c1b53d44ac1a","tid":1181533,"uid":174578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T07:46:32.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: left;\"></div>"},{"pid":"3fa9108a32a8cffeb5a0d1c81c387cfc8f564828","tid":1181533,"uid":174578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T19:28:31.000Z","msg":"<del></del>"},{"pid":"df1f4d96cde2a47c3adbffe39ebaa3f2e3a3029e","tid":1181533,"uid":174578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T05:34:55.000Z","msg":"<strong></strong>"},{"pid":"5eb3fea3be9018e253f8ef54e34f7e55b63d957f","tid":1181533,"uid":174578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T15:22:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">哥布林殺手合作活動６月６日１５００維護後正式開始</span></span>"},{"pid":"888a4ad626d262553648c8f39c06f116d9599f5c","tid":1181533,"uid":174578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T06:28:10.000Z","msg":"<del></del>"},{"pid":"08b7221ef2fe1df174e2b21404a922e36736e48b","tid":1181533,"uid":174578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T07:21:15.000Z","msg":"開ser了"},{"pid":"e88101e87b601e67f46f4632f58b61d6cec834a1","tid":1181533,"uid":174578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T10:23:13.000Z","msg":"<strong></strong>"},{"pid":"2cd9854